{"content":"<div id=\"Ps.127\" class=\"chapter\">\n<h3 class=\"d\">所罗门上行之诗。</h3>\n<h3 class=\"s\">称颂上帝的良善</h3>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v1\"><sup id=\"Ps.127.1\" class=\"v1\">1</sup>若不是耶和华建造房屋，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v1\">建造的人就枉然劳力；</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v1\">若不是耶和华看守城池，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v1\">看守的人就枉然警醒。</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v2\"><sup id=\"Ps.127.2\" class=\"v2\">2</sup>你们清晨早起，夜晚安歇，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v2\">吃劳碌得来的饭，本是枉然；</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v2\">惟有耶和华所亲爱的，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v2\">必叫他安然睡觉。</span></p>\n<p class=\"b\"></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v3\"><sup id=\"Ps.127.3\" class=\"v3\">3</sup>看哪，儿女是耶和华所赐的产业，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v3\">所怀的胎是他所给的赏赐。</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v4\"><sup id=\"Ps.127.4\" class=\"v4\">4</sup>人在年轻时生的儿女</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v4\">好像勇士手中的箭。</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v5\"><sup id=\"Ps.127.5\" class=\"v5\">5</sup>箭袋充满的人有福了！</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v5\">他们在城门口和仇敌争论时必不蒙羞。</span></p>\n</div>\n"}